reviews.review_text: THE BOYS LOVE PHILLY I WILL MAKE THIS SHORT AND SWEET,LISTEN TO THIS IT IS NOT PHENOMINAL LIKE SAY 8/5/74,8/6/74,9/21/72,9/21/73,3/24/73 ALL SHOWS IN PHILA. BUT THIS IS WELL WORTH LISTENING TO.ALSO PEOPLE COMPLAIN ABOUT 1985 AND FOR THE LIFE OF ME I DO NOT KNOW WHY.THERE WAS ONLY A SMALL,SMALL HANDFULL OF WEAK SHOWS BUT MOST ARE STRONG.AND LIKE I SAID BEFORE THE '85 SHOWS IN PHILA. WERE GREAT.
